data.description: Updated southern style home with a sensational screened in back porch in the secluded Northcross subdivision.  This home has character and charm with a grand entrance, formal dining room, home office and large family room.  The kitchen has beautiful white cabinets with gold tone accents and a nearby half bath. Northcross has a split floor plan. The primary room has a large ensuite with jacuzzi tub, marble shower, double vanities and two spacious closets. Bedrooms 2 & 3 are on the other side of the home with a hall bath to share.  New roof HVAC, and hot water heater were replaced in 2021.  X flood zone.  Don't wait - call today to schedule a showing.
